female. A. Anterior head; B. Lateral head and mesosoma; C. Wings; D. Lateral habitus; E. Lateral metasoma.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="D52DFFBA56F063E0C59A444721508B51" pageId="4" pageNumber="141">
